.container.live-reload
  h2.page-sub-title Enabling live-reload
  
  p.text
    | To enable live-reload you have to provide your local dev-server 
    | address to npm's package.json file. Open the package.json file 
    | and edit the proxy field in the config section with your 
    | local dev-server address.

  p.text Example:
  
  pre
    code.snippet
      | "config": {
      |   "proxy": "localhost:8000"
      | }

  br
  p.text 
    | Now you can run npm start to let browser-sync do the live reload:
  
  pre
    code.snippet  
      | npm start
    
